<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Assembled at a Concert for Prayer</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Chihowa ma!
 Chim okla pia kʋt,
 Himak nitak fehna hoka
 Il itahoba cha,
 Pit chim anumpulit,
 Yakohmit e chieyʋshke.

[V2]
 Okla puta moma
 I̱ki chia hak osh
 Et ish i̱ nukha̱klokbano,
 Ahnit, chishno yak o̱
 Pi chu̱kʋsh mominchit
 Isht e chim asihi̱hlʋshke.

[V3]
 Oklushi laua kʋt
 Chim anumpa hoka
 Ik haklo ki̱sha hatuk osh,
 Yoshoba biekʋt,
 Aiokpuloka ma
 Apissanlit maha̱yʋshke.

[V4]
 Ʋba pi̱ Shahli ma!
 Ish i̱ nukha̱klo na,
 Chim anumpa pulla hokʋt
 Chu̱kʋsh fehna hoka
 Nukfoka pullashke,
 Il aiahnishke, Pi̱ki ma!

[V5]
 Oklushi moma kʋt
 Chisʋs chiso hoka
 Immi ha he tok mak oka;
 Ik yʋmohmi pulla,
 Ahnit taloho̱wʋt,
 E chim asilhha fehnʋshke.</lyrics>
<title>Ʋba Chihowa ma! ƲIT104</title>
<time_sig>6.6.8.D.</time_sig>
<hymn_number>104</hymn_number>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
</song>